//-
  To add a new post preview to the feed, I add a new var with 3 preview notes in feed.jade.
  I add a title to var titles and a url to var urls (to the beginning of each array).
  Then I need to replicate a function that generates the 3 previews, with the new var name.
  First one in the code is the newest to show.

include _feed

- var counter = 0
each note in psot.h2
  a(href= "post/#{themes[counter]}/#{urls[counter]}").note-wrapper
    h2= note
      &thinsp;&thinsp;
      span.tag.tag-title.inline-title= titles[counter]

- counter += 1
each note in mews.h2
  a(href= "post/#{themes[counter]}/#{urls[counter]}").note-wrapper
    h2= note
      &thinsp;&thinsp;
      span.tag.tag-title.inline-title= titles[counter]

